to take advantage of her.

13
00:01:58,802 --> 00:02:00,947
She resisted.

14
00:02:00,971 --> 00:02:03,471
She kept her honor.

15
00:02:04,208 --> 00:02:07,234
So they beat her like an animal.

16
00:02:09,180 --> 00:02:12,877
When I went to the hospital,
her nose was broken...

17
00:02:14,185 --> 00:02:16,296
her jaw was shattered...

18
00:02:16,320 --> 00:02:18,820
held together by wire.

19
00:02:20,858 --> 00:02:23,418
She couldn't even weep
because of the pain.

20
00:02:26,263 --> 00:02:29,755
But I wept. Why did I weep?

21
00:02:32,436 --> 00:02:34,936
She was the light of my life.

22
00:02:36,807 --> 00:02:39,307
Beautiful girl.

23
00:02:42,279 --> 00:02:44,779
Now she will never
be beautiful again.

24
00:02:51,922 --> 00:02:54,422
Sorry.

25
00:03:02,566 --> 00:03:05,066
I, I went to the police,
like a good American.

26
00:03:06,136 --> 00:03:08,636
These two boys
were brought to trial.

27
00:03:09,940 --> 00:03:12,704
A judge sentence them
to three years in prison...

28
00:03:12,810 --> 00:03:15,310
and suspend their sentence.

29
00:03:16,113 --> 00:03:18,613
Suspended the sentence.

30
00:03:18,682 --> 00:03:21,182
They went free that very day.

31
00:03:23,354 --> 00:03:25,854
I stood in the courtroom
like a fool.

32
00:03:26,724 --> 00:03:29,989
And those two bastard,
they smiled at me.

33
00:03:31,562 --> 00:03:34,998
Then I said to my wife,
"For justice...

34
00:03:35,099 --> 00:03:37,599
we must go to Don Corleone."

35
00:03:42,506 --> 00:03:45,805
Why did you go to the police?
Why didn't you come to me first?

36
00:03:46,977 --> 00:03:48,788
What do you want of me?

37
00:03:48,812 --> 00:03:51,906
Tell me anything,
but do what I beg you to do.

38
00:03:53,117 --> 00:03:55,617
What is that?

39
00:04:19,510 --> 00:04:22,010
That I cannot do.

40
00:04:22,513 --> 00:04:25,013
I'll give you anything you ask.

41
00:04:27,418 --> 00:04:30,182
We've known each other many years,
but this is the first time...

42
00:04:30,287 --> 00:04:33,620
you ever came to me
for counsel or for help.

43
00:04:33,724 --> 00:04:36,659
I can't remember the last time
that you invited me...

44
00:04:36,760 --> 00:04:39,260
to your house
for a cup of coffee...

45
00:04:40,331 --> 00:04:43,994
even though my wife
is godmother to your only child.

46
00:04:44,101 --> 00:04:46,346
But let's be frank.

47
00:04:46,370 --> 00:04:48,870
You never wanted my friendship...

48
00:04:49,373 --> 00:04:53,002
