to be in my debt.

49
00:04:53,110 --> 00:04:55,610
I didn't want
to get into trouble.

50
00:04:56,714 --> 00:04:59,214
I understand.

51
00:04:59,616 --> 00:05:02,116
You found paradise in America.

52
00:05:04,922 --> 00:05:06,900
You had a good trade,
you made a good living.

53
00:05:06,924 --> 00:05:09,620
Police protected you,
and there were courts of law.

54
00:05:09,727 --> 00:05:12,227
So you didn't need
a friend like me.

55
00:05:14,064 --> 00:05:17,625
But, now you come to me
and you say,

56
00:05:17,735 --> 00:05:20,235
"Don Corleone, give me justice."

57
00:05:21,972 --> 00:05:24,839
But you don't ask with respect.

58
00:05:24,942 --> 00:05:27,502
You don't offer friendship.

59
00:05:27,611 --> 00:05:30,111
