173
00:14:35,425 --> 00:14:37,925
he found Tom Hagen in the street,
and he had no home.

174
00:14:38,828 --> 00:14:41,328
And so my father took him in...

175
00:14:41,898 --> 00:14:44,398
and he's been with us ever since.

176
00:14:45,101 --> 00:14:47,601
